OL,5, A draft report uncovered by the BBC    
OL,6, shows the Post Office spent #100m      
OL,7, fighting sub-postmasters in court      
OL,8, despite knowing its defence was untrue.
OL,10,FThe document reveals the Post Office   
OL,11,Fwas shown evidence by 2017 that losses 
OL,12,Fcould be due to errors in the Horizon  
OL,13,FIT system or remote tampering.         
OL,15,FBut it kept arguing in the Bates v Post
OL,16,FOffice Ltd case that theft or mistakes 
OL,17,Fby sub-postmasters must be to blame.   
OL,19,FThe Post Office said it would be       
OL,20,F"inappropriate" to comment.            
